    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly such a great find. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in wonderful shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road. It drives super smoothly and has been a total joy to own! I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
