    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe, a comprehensive Vanos rebuild, and rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells. The suspension geometry is tight, benefiting from refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and compression across all cylinders\u2014are within factory specifications. A mechanically robust specimen for the purist.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
