      "description": "This refined luxury sedan represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking both performance and reliability. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic charcoal that still catches the light beautifully, showing only minor stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the heated leather seats are supple and free of tears, and the walnut wood trim retains its original luster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the vehicle has been maintained with an open checkbook policy, featuring a recently documented oil service, new spark plugs, and tires with approximately 80% tread remaining. It delivers a smooth, composed ride with the responsive handling these models are known for. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been kept in consistent mechanical health and is ready for many more miles of enjoyment.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
